    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tracery whose openings are or seem to be pierced through slabs of stone; used especially in Early Gothic windows.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
